Capemusic, I knew I was forgetting to comment on something. Here's my problem.  Because those labels support Artists, I typically list those albums, not under "Hosanna", but rather under the Artist's name. For example, Don Moen has done lots with Hosanna, so I list those albums as "Don Moen."  And because of that, it's now nearly impossible for me to now determine if, and where, my Hosanna / Integrity albums are.  :(
